description: This header file declares functions for managing telephony numbering plans, including getting and setting parameters, retrieving entry counts, and accessing entries related to number prefixes.

methods.name: NumberingPlan_GetParamUlongValue
methods.description: Retrieves a ULONG parameter value for the specified numbering plan context.

methods.name: NumberingPlan_SetParamUlongValue
methods.description: Sets a ULONG parameter value for the specified numbering plan context.

methods.name: PrefixInfo_GetEntryCount
methods.description: Returns the total number of prefix entries available.

methods.name: PrefixInfo_GetEntry
methods.description: Retrieves a specific prefix entry based on the index.

methods.name: PrefixInfo_GetParamUlongValue
methods.description: Retrieves a ULONG parameter value for a specific prefix info context.

methods.name: PrefixInfo_SetParamUlongValue
methods.description: Sets a ULONG parameter value for a specific prefix info context.

methods.name: PrefixInfo_GetParamStringValue
methods.description: Retrieves a string parameter value for a specific prefix info context.

methods.name: PrefixInfo_SetParamStringValue
methods.description: Sets a string parameter value for a specific prefix info context.
